<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.9">
<l>eṉṉaim pulaṉu meḻiluṅkoṇ ṭiṅkē neruna leḻuntaruḷi</l>
<l>poṉṉaṅ kalaikaḷ meliveytap pōṉa puṉita rūrpōlum</l>
<l>maṉṉu mutunī raravinta malarmēl varivaṇ ṭicaipāṭa</l>
<l>aṉṉam peṭaiyō ṭuṭaṉāṭu maṇiyār vayalcū ḻaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the pure one who, having graciously appearing here yesterday,</l>
<l>Taking my five senses and beauty, then left,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that my lovely, elegant sari got limp,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr surrounded by beautiful fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where a swan and [its] mate dance together,</l>
<l>As striped bees, on lotus blossoms in the long-established waters,</l>
<l rend="indent">sing melodies.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
